    "abstract": "<jats:title>Abstract</jats:title>\n                <jats:p>Using electronic health record data combined with primary chart review, we identified 7 children across 8 pediatric medical centers with a diagnosis of Multisystem Inflammatory Syndrome in Children (MIS-C) who were managed as outpatients. These findings should prompt a discussion about modifying the case definition to allow for such a possibility.</jats:p>",
